This repository ("compile-time-browser" / ctbrowser) is a derivative
work built on:

    compile-time-html  (cthtml)  https://github.com/alexios-angel/compile-time-html
    compile-time-javascript (ctjs)  https://github.com/alexios-angel/compile-time-javascript
    compile-time-css   (ctcss)  https://github.com/alexios-angel/compile-time-css

each of which is built on:

    notre (a fork of Compile Time Regular Expressions)
    https://github.com/alexios-angel/notre

which is itself a derivative of:

